-36 overflow-hidden\"><img alt=\"橄欖油護膚的分子美學：為什麼角鯊烯（Squalene）是您肌膚最親密的仿生防護盾？ — 知橄生活 Olive Wisdom\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"https://picture-search.skywork.ai/skills/upload/2026-04-17/6121d0fbc8a3466fb8557d5fc8af1e45_0f0b7.png\"/></div><div class=\"p-4\"><h3 class=\"text-sm font-bold text-olive-800 line-clamp-2 group-hover:text-olive-600 transition-colors\">橄欖油護膚的分子美學：為什麼角鯊烯（Squalene）是您肌膚最親密的仿生防護盾？</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-2\">7<!-- --> 分鐘閱讀</p></div></article></a><a class=\"group\" href=\"/blog/mediterranean-diet-anti-aging-women-2026/\"><article class=\"bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-all overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"relative h-36 overflow-hidden\"><img alt=\"地中海飲食與女性抗衰老：科學實證的每日飲食策略 — 知橄生活 Olive Wisdom\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-300\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"https://picture-search.skywork.ai/skills/upload/2026-04-17/4e13ed9b8d55434daf1db0fe2d809af1_7e605.png\"/></div><div class=\"p-4\"><h3 class=\"text-sm font-bold text-olive-800 line-clamp-2 group-hover:text-olive-600 transition-colors\">地中海飲食與女性抗衰老：科學實證的每日飲食策略</h3><p class=\"text-xs text-gray-400 mt-2\">7<!-- --> 分鐘閱讀</p></div></article></a></div></div></section></main><!--$--><!--/$--></div><footer class=\"bg-olive-900 text-olive-200\"><div class=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-8 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 md:gap-8\"><div class=\"md:col-span-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-3\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🫒</span><div><p class=\"font-bold text-white text-sm\">知橄生活</p><p class=\"text-xs text-olive-400 tracking-widest uppercase\">Olive Wisdom</p></div></d